<problem id="fs-id1170571051867">
<para id="fs-id1170571051869">Show that <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msup><m:mi>e</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mn>−2</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> solves this initial-value problem.</para>
